summary: Code tries to convert a string to an integer and checks if it's possible. If successful, it prints "possible" and breaks the loop; otherwise, it increments the counter and prints "not working". This process is repeated three times before exiting.

details.comment: Code tries to convert a string to an integer and checks if it's possible. If successful, it prints "possible" and breaks the loop; otherwise, it increments the counter and prints "not working". This process is repeated three times before exiting.
details.content:
